oc:kn_36194388 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When user specifies audience type" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Select template based on audience: Individual template for managers, Team Rollup for team leads, Executive Summary for leadership, Client Progress for external stakeholders." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Different audiences need different levels of detail, focus areas, and formality" .

oc:kn_3bec0aa2 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When describing blockers in any report template" ;
    oc:directiveContent "For blockers, always specify: the issue, its impact (delays/dependencies), what help is needed, and any attempted solutions." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Incomplete blocker descriptions prevent stakeholders from taking effective action" .

oc:kn_4a7f7f3b a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Always — this skill is purely generative" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Reports cannot access actual work systems, calendars, or project management tools. All content must be provided by the user." ;
    oc:hasRationale "The skill has no system integrations; it relies entirely on user-provided information" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_7599c5d0 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating a report" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Offer customization on length (brief/standard/detailed), tone (casual/formal), focus areas, and frequency adaptation (daily/bi-weekly/monthly)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Organizations have varied reporting norms; flexibility increases adoption" .

oc:kn_bf49a6a9 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When writing accomplishments section of any report" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Do not use vague activity descriptions like 'Worked on X'. Instead use action verbs (Completed, Delivered, Launched, Resolved) with specific, quantified outcomes." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Vague descriptions fail to communicate value and make it hard for stakeholders to assess progress" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

